> Dear Richard,
>
> Your (*) is not an additional condition. Being a sheaf for both J and J'
> is equivalent to being a sheaf for their join (which I presume is what you
> mean by J n J'). For a proof, see A4.5.16 in the Elephant.
>
> Peter
